Invocation Name: food fun facts
des: This skill, "Food Fun Facts," provides fun facts about food. It includes some facts that may have not been known by many. To activate the skill, one must simply say, "tell me a food fact." There are no prerequisite for this skill as it can be accessed by any Echo device and the Alexa app.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
